{"word":"πάππος","slug":"πάππος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πάππος</b></el> <el>(πάππος, ὁ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>akin to <el>πάππας</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a grandfather</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>: —in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <i>one's grand-parents, ancestors</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>a little bird, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}